---
title: Philly-Style Portobello Hoagies with Potato Wedges and Spicy Mayo
description: Meaty portobello mushrooms are the perfect stand-in for steaks in our vegetarian version of this Philly classic. We've even got you covered with a spicy sriracha mayo dip to go with the sweet potato wedges!
